  "prompt": "Why did Quora acquire Parlio?",
  "response": "Quora acquired Parlio in March 2016 to strengthen its platform and expand its reach in the domain of sharing knowledge and fostering discussions. Parlio was a platform focused on facilitating meaningful conversations and engaging communities, much like Quora, and this acquisition aimed to bolster Quora\u2019s capabilities in these areas. The acquisition provided Quora with additional intellectual assets, user base, and innovative features that complemented its mission of building a global knowledge-sharing community. Additionally, bringing Parlio\u2019s team into the fold was seen as an opportunity to enhance Quora\u2019s talent pool and potentially accelerate its growth and development strategies.",
